section.para:
Since application/json has no provisions for linking, we can't use it as a hypermedia format.
In other words, you can use JSON for REST maturity levels 0, 1, and 2, but not for levels 3a, 3b, or 4 (see 
). To get to level 3a, we need to add linking capabilities.

